<h3>1、安装 Toolbox</h3>

<p>最新版 Toolbox&nbsp;下载地址：&nbsp;<a href="https://www.docker.com/get-docker" target="_blank">https://www.docker.com/get-docker</a></p>

<p>点击&nbsp;<a href="https://www.docker.com/community-edition" target="_blank">Get Docker Community Edition</a>，并下载 Windows 的版本：</p>

<p><img src="http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/A5C273D6-FED1-49AC-A26B-99CD2D2CFE47.jpg" /></p>

